================
Django Buildhost
================



Initialize host
---------------

user.init_home_env:8081



Add environment
---------------

fab -H sudoer@hostname bh.root.init_env

fab -H sudoer@hostname bh.root.user_create:<USERNAME>,[<PASSWORD>]

fab -H <USERNAME>@<HOST> bh.user.init_home_env:<PORT>

fab -H <USERNAME>@<HOST> bh.system.sqlite bh.system.python bh.system.apache bh.system.modwsgi bh.system.oracle bh.system.sqlplus



Examples
--------

fab -H user@host system.sqlite system.python system.apache system.modwsgi system.oracle system.sqlplus
